Package: rnirs
Type: Package
Title: Locally Weighted PLS Regressions and Other Methods for Near Infrared Spectral Data
Version: 1.0-4
Author: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Maintainer: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Description: Statistical tool box for near infrared spectral data with a focus on locally weighted prediction methods.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: scales, signal, data.table, FNN, ggplot2, gridExtra 
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
URL: https://github.com/mlesnoff/rnirs
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: yes
